    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于 &quot;圣诞节&quot;礼包</h2><br>请注意该武器系列外观很有特别。如果你喜欢时髦的武器，或者简直不能不消灭敌人，这把武器一定会让你满意。你的角色会引起所有战士的注意。<br><br>高系列包括8个职业头盔，背心，手套，战鞋。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/120613c9c302e0dc7f0b1a5b84900792.poster.avif?t=1685625804\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/120613c9c302e0dc7f0b1a5b84900792.webm?t=1685625804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/120613c9c302e0dc7f0b1a5b84900792.mp4?t=1685625804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >圣诞节步枪手头盔</h2>步枪手头盔提高头部护甲值为30%，闪光弹致盲效果降低40%。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/300dd6085cc7ff41b3a7fb70cfd94215.avif?t=1685625804\" width=616 height=256 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >圣诞节医疗兵头盔</h2>步枪手头盔提高头部护甲值为30%，闪光弹致盲效果降低40%。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/b5626875d6b7b7c13ff85315b9450e03.avif?t=1685625804\" width=616 height=256 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >圣诞节工程师头盔</h2>步枪手头盔提高头部护甲值为30%，也可以在10m距离之内发现敌人地雷。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/edf04c62c788cc940997358444b52ded.avif?t=1685625804\" width=616 height=256 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >圣诞节狙击手头盔</h2>步枪手头盔提高头部护甲值为30%，闪光弹致盲效果降低40%。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/3f7c5839713e1769ef3eab4e3fc0a0d6.avif?t=1685625804\" width=616 height=256 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >可怕步枪手头盔</h2>步枪手头盔提高头部护甲值为60%，闪光弹致盲效果降低40%，也可以在10m距离之内发现敌人地雷。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/163f698da6a9e577f2de3325f1b3d807.avif?t=1685625804\" width=616 height=256 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >可怕医疗兵头盔</h2>步枪手头盔提高头部护甲值为30%，闪光弹致盲效果降低40%，也可以在10m距离之内发现敌人地雷。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/f12044a58deaae25ecc52087ed4796cf.avif?t=1685625804\" width=616 height=256 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >可怕工程师头盔</h2>步枪手头盔提高头部护甲值为50%，闪光弹致盲效果降低40%，也可以在10m距离之内发现敌人地雷。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/25f5f3364ec43d176d072777cb101ce8.avif?t=1685625804\" width=616 height=256 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >可怕狙击手头盔</h2>步枪手头盔提高头部护甲值为50%，闪光弹致盲效果降低40%，也可以在10米距离之内发现敌人地雷。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/491d5a984b34a5b1de4f3692b3567ad4.avif?t=1685625804\" width=616 height=256 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >万圣节背心</h2>具有135护甲值点数，吸收子弹伤害为10点，减少爆炸伤害为25%，提高提高武器容量为1.5倍。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/d046fb80f97e23b178936371b028287b.avif?t=1685625804\" width=616 height=256 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >万圣节手套</h2>提高换弹和更改武器速度为20%。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/03af06c3b6ffb5f3b4decbff999fa0b4.avif?t=1685625804\" width=616 height=256 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >万圣节战鞋</h2>提高冲刺速度和时间为15%和10%。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/e535330ace5b192288eb40be2ab5bc75.avif?t=1685625804\" width=616 height=256 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于 &quot;特工&quot;礼包</h2><br>“冰川”礼包中有多彩的外观和有趣的武器动画。小心点 - 冷极了！<br><br>礼包中有6把武器和一把刀。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Cobalt Kinetics EDGE Rifle &quot;冰川&quot;</h2>这是 是一款由科伯特动力公司研制的现代时尚铝制步枪，采用了双栓控制。轻便且符合人体工程学，为使用者提供了一流的控制性能、精准度和火力。大部分情况下武器能够一射就击杀敌人，而5件配件可以帮你更快消灭敌人。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/d32fba1c6a5f1ec56300855121756eb9.poster.avif?t=1685625804\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/d32fba1c6a5f1ec56300855121756eb9.webm?t=1685625804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/d32fba1c6a5f1ec56300855121756eb9.mp4?t=1685625804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/f03ddd93eb05ad214e66080dbdf1d34e.avif?t=1685625804\" width=616 height=256 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Typhoon F12 Custom &quot;冰川&quot;</h2>台风 F12 是一把顶尖的弹匣供弹战术霰弹枪！武器有效率很高，玩家不用担心有人会在近战呐过程中及杀他，他的武器一定会保护他。 武器属性平衡特别好，在任何情况下都很好用。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/ae60a002070c9dff0d404e3ab8a5d9e7.poster.avif?t=1685625804\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/ae60a002070c9dff0d404e3ab8a5d9e7.webm?t=1685625804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/ae60a002070c9dff0d404e3ab8a5d9e7.mp4?t=1685625804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/388eb8a8d91716e9e49b6ebf90652a42.avif?t=1685625804\" width=616 height=256 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Cobalt Kinetics Stealth Pistol &quot;冰川&quot;</h2>该款新型隐形手枪作为科伯特动力公司产品阵容的最新成员，是该公司首屈一指的武器。该款隐形手枪结构紧凑、平衡性极佳、威力大、精准度高且适应性强。Cobalt Kinetics Stealth Pistol 有许多配件，都会把武器变为更致命。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/66ccaebc33321d0819e8acbbdae335a7.poster.avif?t=1685625804\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/66ccaebc33321d0819e8acbbdae335a7.webm?t=1685625804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/66ccaebc33321d0819e8acbbdae335a7.mp4?t=1685625804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/7d3a53b11c142dccb31cb0c123c37276.avif?t=1685625804\" width=616 height=256 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Cobalt Kinetics Twenty-Seven &quot;冰川&quot;</h2>由科伯特动力公司特别研制的武器，结合了猎枪的经典特色和配备快慢机的现代步枪的便利性。你可以随时根据自己的射击姿势来配置伸缩式枪托。武器所有配件可以被玩家调整。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/d6e568902db973eac8698de5bdd3d12c.poster.avif?t=1685625804\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/d6e568902db973eac8698de5bdd3d12c.webm?t=1685625804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/d6e568902db973eac8698de5bdd3d12c.mp4?t=1685625804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/5727b65caa9df84d841575d256c77c2a.avif?t=1685625804\" width=616 height=256 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >M134-GAU19b Hybrid &quot;冰川&quot;</h2>这种机枪重量较轻，专为轻型 SED 战队研制，射速快，火力猛。不过，必须小心监测这款武器的温度，因为它会比 SED 使用的其他机枪更快出现过热的情况。M134-GAU19b Hybrid武器可以过热，玩家一定应该小心，不能长时间之内一直用它。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/95d4398526b29299bbfc3ebdb235f4a7.avif?t=1685625804\" width=616 height=256 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Kel-Tec SUB2000 &quot;冰川&quot;</h2>SUB2000 是一款由 Kel-Tec 制造的 9 毫米轻量级卡宾枪。这款枪最显著的特点就是可以对折，轻松收入包中。采用人体工程学设计，射击精准，输出火力成本低。武器属性相当于家喻户晓的武器：Mateba Autorevolver 和 S&amp;W M&amp;P R8.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/9a901c8ca021524ca1f7375fcd38b466.avif?t=1685625804\" width=616 height=256 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HX Outdoors Trident &quot;冰川&quot;</h2>X Outdoors Trident 刀的刀刃固定，非常适合用于生存。这把刀力量大，硬度高，防腐耐磨。采用符合人体工程学的复合纤维防腐防滑刀把！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/95b99817db037dc9e304c33d9b55749e.avif?t=1685625804\" width=616 height=256 /></span><br><br>理所当然，你可以通过使用这些武器来得到多样成就。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/d95ba20e3e512b7658593a373471f2d8.avif?t=1685625804\" width=616 height=256 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于”狙击枪”套装</h2><br>该武器系列武器表面上有多样的冰雪花纹，但同时让武器变得越来越强大。这些武器外观风格很有特点，把战场便成为圣诞节气氛节日场面！<br><br>该礼包中有多样的武器，在任何情况下都很好用。<br><br>武器中有5把武器和一把刀，你的敌人都避免不了。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SAI GRY AR-15 &quot;霜&quot;</h2>SAI GRY AR-15 的的现代化版本，配有双弹鼓、符合人体工程学的突击手握把和抑制器。武器伤害很高，此外武器可以给肢体造成更多伤害。 武器容量不错，射击速度特别高，瞄准模式中精度也很不错。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/40c947ee9a8884b76f85ce710eb7964c.poster.avif?t=1685625804\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/40c947ee9a8884b76f85ce710eb7964c.webm?t=1685625804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/40c947ee9a8884b76f85ce710eb7964c.mp4?t=1685625804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/5cc6d3f05fe02b023e497dcd922b7e43.avif?t=1685625804\" width=616 height=256 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SAP6 &quot;霜&quot;</h2>短管 SAP6 弹匣供弹式重装霰弹枪。它的新设计特色包含一个重装单体式四轨系统和一个经过重新设计的铝质泵握把，配合内置垂直前握把使用。MAG-7和Fabarm STF 12 Compact是他的主要竞争对手。可拆卸式弹匣的使用确保能在不牺牲弹匣容量的前提下，让枪管更短。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/8611cda3679442a14ca926ea5cd80f73.poster.avif?t=1685625804\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/8611cda3679442a14ca926ea5cd80f73.webm?t=1685625804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/8611cda3679442a14ca926ea5cd80f73.mp4?t=1685625804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/941a569d8339dde973841f314c331a18.avif?t=1685625804\" width=616 height=256 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Uzi Pro &quot;霜&quot;</h2>UZI PRO 是传奇的 UZI 系列的最新成员，UZI 是全世界最受欢迎的武器系列，在全球已售出几百万套。UZI PRO 是执法机关、要员保镖以及特种部队隐蔽携带或公开使用的理想枪支。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/13195349a406e5c771e389d94c7762b4.poster.avif?t=1685625804\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/13195349a406e5c771e389d94c7762b4.webm?t=1685625804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/13195349a406e5c771e389d94c7762b4.mp4?t=1685625804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/efc62b465afa2950ccd16d7ef7486602.avif?t=1685625804\" width=616 height=256 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gepard GM6 Lynx &quot;霜&quot;</h2>猎豹 GM6 Lynx 是一款匈牙利半自动反器材步枪. 它采用无托结构和伸缩枪管，对于有着如此火力的武器来说，它的造型相当紧凑。这把枪的重量分布也使得人们可以采用无依托立姿操作它，这对于其它大口径步枪来说要困难的多。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/1c6a878d5e060284b76901877c676a28.poster.avif?t=1685625804\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/1c6a878d5e060284b76901877c676a28.webm?t=1685625804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/1c6a878d5e060284b76901877c676a28.mp4?t=1685625804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/e308f2135e7038f2ad9ac651387189c1.avif?t=1685625804\" width=616 height=256 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MPA 930DMG &quot;霜&quot;</h2>MPA 930DMG 是一款高度符合人体工程学的全自动手枪，特别合适喜欢PvP战斗的玩家：这把枪允许你很快造成爆头，消灭敌人。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/8a326cbfeb05dd0fe92a1a24928423b3.avif?t=1685625804\" width=616 height=256 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >M48 Bowie &quot;霜&quot;</h2>M48 是久经考验的鲍威刀的现代重现版，它具备坚固的不锈钢刀刃、锯齿状的刀背和钛金属外壳。此武器可充分满足你所有的炫酷需求。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/4d0b3968f614cfb4b4c8465c55985cbe.poster.avif?t=1685625804\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/4d0b3968f614cfb4b4c8465c55985cbe.webm?t=1685625804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/4d0b3968f614cfb4b4c8465c55985cbe.mp4?t=1685625804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/26e63d1e7c97db3d2cc54d78d22a1af3.avif?t=1685625804\" width=616 height=256 /></span><br><br>理所当然，你可以通过使用这些武器来得到多样成就。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753630/extras/e3e480673457eaffb4b8e0131d25ed98.avif?t=1685625804\" width=616 height=256 /></span><br><br>支付好之后请稍等15分钟左右。如果物品还没到账的话，请重新启动游戏。 所有物品都是永久版的。",
